    <h1>Discover Greece</h1>
    <p><strong>Greece</strong> <em>(Ellada),</em> officially the <strong>Hellenic Republic</strong>, also known as <strong>Hellas</strong>, is a country located in Southeast Europe.</p>

    <p>There are <em>18 UNESCO World Heritage Sites in Greece,</em> and Greece is ranked 16th in the world in terms of total sites.</p>

